     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <head>Ad LECTOREM.</head>
   <l>SI variis gaudes, miranda, recondita quaeris;</l>
   <l>Si peregrina cupis, splendida, rara, bona;</l>
   <l>Si leges, artes, &amp; quae Coelestia spectant;</l>
   <l>Si manes, mores, Physica, mentis opes;</l>
   <l>Hoc opus eximium, ex cunctis praestantia pandet:</l>
   <l>Perlege, vix aliud talia, tanta dabit.</l>
   <l>Liv<gap reason="illegible" resp="#tech" extent="1 letter">
         <desc>•</desc>
      </gap>r summa petens carpat; sed carpitur ipse</l>
   <l>Irradiante libri lumine, ne invideat.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>Io. Episco. <hi>Cathanesius.</hi>
      </signed>
   </closer>
</div>
